init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He then informs her that he's going to be away for a couple of weeks, and to use his credit card to buy things she likes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He pulls the curtains shut and climbs into bed with Christina.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As fake Elon Musk sleeps, Christina wakes up and quietly opens her purse.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She hears a faint voice from behind the door.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The voice behind the door gets louder and clearer, "Help me!"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He looks like he hasn't bathed in months.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She asks the real Elon Musk.
